|GKO================================================================
                       |MKBKiss of Helios
|GKO================================================================

|YKOIt was in the middle of the great warrior's visionquest that Helios,
the God of the Sun, came to Refa. He explained to the Garou how to invoke
the spirit of the sun. With this skill, a Garou can invoke the sun's 
power to ignite a portion of his body and keep it burning for extended 
periods. Most commonly the Garou will light his mane during the ritual,
without suffering ill effect.  The blessing conferred is short-term,
and is only useful in a Garou's wolven form. A fire elemental or a 
sun-spirit teaches this Gift currently.

|WKOUsable in Form: |GKOCrinos and Wolf only
|WKORestricted to: |GKBGuardian
|RKOSyntax: |YKBflames      |WKOCost: |CKOvaried

|WKBNOTE: This ability shows in the 'buffs' command. It can be ended
early with 'clearbuff'. This ability cannot be used in conjunction with 
the skill 'quills'.
